
reZet80 PIONEER R1 Changelog [last modified: 2023-01-10]
--------------------------------------------------------

Changes in reZet80 PIONEER R1 release:
- Introduced Intel 8279 Programmable Keyboard/Display Interface
- Extended 7-segment LED display to 16 characters
- First reZet80 game: Haunted House text adventure
- Alphanumericals ("0"-"9", "A"-"Z") and punctuation symbols are available
- Moved to rasm assembler because of support for undocumented instructions
- Provide binary ROM and Intel hex format
